query:
-- Get California protocol counts by county
SELECT 
    c.name as agency_name,
    COUNT(p.id) as protocol_count
FROM counties c
LEFT JOIN protocolChunks p ON c.id = p.countyId
WHERE c.state = 'California'
    AND c.name IN ('San Diego County EMS', 'Orange County EMS Agency', 'Sacramento County EMS Agency')
GROUP BY c.id, c.name
ORDER BY protocol_count DESC;
